data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Great 3 bedroom 2 bath block home conveniently located near Maitland interchange (414), RDV Sports Center, I-4 and less than 30 minutes to downtown.  Featuring an open plan with living room kitchen combo.  The Kitchen was remodeled in 2015 with new cabinets, granite counter tops and stainless appliances. Other updates in 2015 include bathrooms, flooring, roof, windows and ac. Plus this home also offers a carport, storage room, back uncovered patio, large treed lot and NO HOA.  Great for rental too.  Seller to contribute $5000 towards closing costs, updates or repairs. Sold AS IS.
